description:
Sweet Tooth Vol. 01 - Out of the Deep Woods (2010) (TPB) (Digital-Empire)


The first five issues of Jeff Lemire's acclaimed series introduce Gus, a rare new breed of human/animal hybrid who was raised in isolation following a pandemic that struck a decade earlier. Now, with the death of his father, he's left to fend for himself . . . until he meets a hulking drifter named Jepperd, who promises to help him. Jepperd and Gus set out on a post-apocalyptic journey into the devastated American landscape to find 'The Preserve,' a refuge for hybrids
